Name: stardoc
URL: https://github.com/bazelbuild/stardoc
Version: 0.8.1
Revision: 58f90b8c564891b0888929e56c8c0116c9420eb4

License File: LICENSE.txt

Description: Stardoc is a tool to generate documentation for Bazel rules.
Local Modifications: We cannot use stardoc directly because it uses rules_java which our
build does not support. Instead, we use the new rule that is introduced
in bazel 7.0 which extracts docs into a protobuf. This is what stardoc
is doing under the hood.
